Package: pepVet
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate Proteolytic Digests for Proteomics Workflows
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R:
    person("Enes K. Ergin", email = "eneskemalergin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for simulating proteolytic digestion and scoring
    peptide sets for proteomics workflows. The package currently provides
    validated digest generation, amino-acid reference data, and a core
    scoring engine for summarizing peptide suitability at the protein level.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/LangeLab/pepVet, https://langelab.github.io/pepVet/
BugReports: https://github.com/LangeLab/pepVet/issues
